fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 gained 119.35 points or 0.68% to settle at 17,743.40. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, rose 0.32% to 11.67. ICICI Bank, RIL and HDFC Bank were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The April 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 27 April 2023.
